      • setRightX

        public final GObject setRightX(float rightX)
        Sets the object's rightmost x-coordinate to be the given value. This does not resize the object but moves it as though you had set its leftmost x-coordinate to rightX - getWidth().

      • setBottomY

        public final GObject setBottomY(float bottomY)
        Sets the object's bottom y-coordinate to be the given value. This does not resize the object but moves it as though you had set its top y-coordinate to bottomY - getHeight().
